name: RData
source:
$@import fileinfo, file

$@input name, character, description = "Name of the variable to hold this table."

$@page p1, "Import Settings"

$@input x

$@if fileinfo$ext == "RData"
load(fileinfo$path)
$@end-if

$@output Environment, print

for (name in ls())
    cat(name, class(get(name)), "\n")
